It is easy to say that "earthquake prediction from planetary alignment has been disproven."

But scientists have not studied the relationship between specific planetary alignments and larger earthquakes.

SSGEOS has done this study and developed #SSGI to prove this relationship. https://t.co/pGFv62h4WN

Conservatives need to stop using the 13/51 meme. It's statistically inaccurate.

column3: Math is wrong. Subtracting “Unknown” from “Total”, which only includes offenders where race is known, makes no sense and makes the result much larger.    Correct calculation is:    7,875/(7,875+4,905+1,941+165+95)=52.6%    Note: Current FBI data slightly different but result same.    https://cde.ucr.cjis.gov/LATEST/webapp/#/pages/explorer/crime/crime-trend
